summary:
*Need the original MOD!*
More Black looks for Iorveth Armor by Hucifer, CD Projekt Red(well...), and L0rd0fWar.
descriptionHtml:
Done By Request.

Well; It\'s quite funny that this is my first mod upload every in whole nexus...


Installation:
1. Download the original mod 
Link: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5644
2. Install the original mod, then download this retex.
3. Unzip(7z) and overwrite the original mod\'s texture folder with this.
4. Give Endorsements to; Link: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5644





Pics would be uploaded soon!
